extends ../layouts/layout_small

block content
  .xs-container
    form(action='/signin', method='post')
      .page-header
        h2 로그인
        p.text-danger= message
      .form-group.form-group-lg
        label(for='email') Email Address
        input#email.form-control(type='email', placeholder='Email', required='', autofocus='', tabindex='1' name='email')
        span.help-block
      .form-group.form-group-lg
        label(for='password') Password
        span.text-right(tabindex='5')
          a.text-info(href='/find') 비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?
        input#password.form-control(type='password', placeholder='Password', required='', tabindex='2' name='password')
        span.help-block
      button#btn-login.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-block(type='submit', tabindex='3') 로그인
      p.go-signup 아이오 교육센터 회원이 아니세요?  
        a.text-hightitle(href='/signup', tabindex='4') 회원가입